Package: investdatar
Title: Investment Data Access and Preparation Toolkit
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Oliver", "Lee", email = "olee7149@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolkit for loading, transforming, and managing 
    structured investment-related data. Includes functions for retrieving 
    macroeconomic series from FRED, detecting gaps in market candle data, 
    and syncing datasets between local machines and cloud VMs. Provides 
    utilities for working with crypto exchange data (e.g., OKX) and preparing 
    time-aligned datasets for analysis and trading.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    data.table,
    jsonlite,
    curl
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
